ChangeHistory.Change: Fixed ESM test and Trailer Brake Switch Test, other minor adjustments
Disabled dual coax PIP test due to PIP switch on both connectors broken
Added tester present scheduled message to ESM for reading DTC's
Added DTC for two way shifter lever
Adjusted lower limit for courtesty foot well lamps. Changed logic for sdar connector from RSD-TBM to RSD!TBM
Changd TBM to TBM disabled 1 ITBM Test
Change timer and removed duplicate prompt lables
Changed pass window for Bower delta read
ITBM disabled press and hold minus replaced with press plus
Added second ITBM switch test back in
Changed order of the test and wait for timer to 25 sec
Moved Speaker Test, GPS Coax, GPS CELL, GPS CELL, AM/FM Antenna, ELT Headlamp Switch above Timer Complete.
Increased WaitForTimerToExpire (Timer Complete) from 30 Seconds to 35 Seconds to give CMCM time to Responde (was giving 7F)
Change tester present and extended diag test for board 1 and 2
Changed sales code for HVAC actuators
Changed AM/FM Coax Diconnect from incorrect Ch 10 on ModBus 1 to Ch 11 ModBus 1.
Removed CMCM read DTC. Radio returnimng a negative response. Updated LED Courtesy upper test limit from 6 volts to 8 volts.
Changed lower test limits for airbag testing from 0 to 1.8 ohms.
Moved HVAC clear DTC to after CAN validation test step
Changed sunload sensor and cabin temperature sensor DTC descriptions. They were swapped.
Updated HVAC DTC desriptions with hex to DTC code conversion in the descriptions.
Corrected AM/FM test channel. Board 2 channel 12 Updated LED Courtesy lamp limits.
updated blower mod code from Blower to BLOWER
turned off hvac message after testing
Seperated the CELL and GPS coax tests
Updated Actuator Descriptions, added connector number
Added D023 and D028 message for the 2 actuators that used to be DTC's, not read position
Re - enabled HVAC mode 2 act test

Adjusted actuator test limits to include FF
00 when disconnected
Added duct sensor temp read trial
added duct sensor left read temp trial
Cleaned up and re-added the duct sensor temp read test
Adjusted limits of right floor temp read, using byte 4 instead of byte 5
Added &!WDICSPS to the WD ICS for the part shortage
Added Commands to move the Front Mode 1, Front Mode 2, Recirc, Main Left & Right Temp actuators
Disabled Recirc door testing. Not a reliable test always reads FF
Changed the range for the righ temp actuator frm 01-FE to 00-1E
Changed thebyte range to 03-FF for all actuators. When unplugged they go to 0,
Updated descriptions for HVAC DTC to included connector #, Update fault descriptions on the lights to include the connector #
Changed test step timeout from 20 seconds to 30 seconds for the trailer brake switch testing. Per Akshay Patil
Updated speaker option code from "Speaker" to RCA|RC3
Updated some of the repair lines
Removed duplicate test for the Left Temp Door Actuator
Changed some of the CAN module descriptions
Cleaned up fault lines for Part Numbers and DTC checks
Added Fatal faults after the airbags and the SGW
Added Software Check for the CMCM
Changed the script on the CMCM part number to verify both the root and nic are correct
Changed the TTO for HVAC clear DTC to 1000 and extended timeout to 5000ms
Added Sales code 2023 to the cmcm part number with the nic and software check
Disable the CMCM Tester Present scheduled message before part number checks.
